::DrillBit::

"I'll ask KillFest, and DarkFate. In a minute."
He knew what was wrong, she missed the Command spot.
He placed a hand on her cheek.
"Dont look so down, love. It doesn't suit someone with your looks."
He smiled, and kissed her.

::Hot Rod::

"Ok, recap. Maximal Matrix turns me good. I try to stay with you.
Alliance reprograms you to forget me. As soon as I'm starting to bring
back your memories, Zardus gets suspecious, and tryes to kill me. Thats
why I'm here. I cant come there because You'll be meeting scrap metal
then. We need a place thats not in our sides territory."
He then hears the other part.
"New form? I can wait."

OOC: For sentamental purposes, Feline still has the Autobot pilot
'wings' that Hot Rod gave her.
